Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.43,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:30.60,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Damn, he climbed up the\Nslope as if it was a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何と
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,路肩の斜面をバンク替わりに駆け上がるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.60,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この目で見たものは信じられないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.97,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't believe what I just saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.55,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If he forced the car\Nto stay on the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無理にコースに留まろうとあがけば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.29,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...it would have hit the curb and\Nbounced back uncontrollably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,縁石にはねられてとっちらかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:50.16,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{tate}He aimed straight for the slope,\Ninstead of trying to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,立てなおそうとせずに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,土手をめがけてまっすぐに駆け上がった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:55.40,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{tossa}It was a split-second decision. It would\Nhave been too late if he tried to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とっさの反応なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,考えていてはとても間に合わない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:07:00.83,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's even more of a natural than\Nthat downhiller, Fujiwara Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ダウンヒルの藤原拓海に輪をかけるほどのナチュラルっぷりだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちー 運の強い男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:12.37,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You have strong luck,\Nbut how long will it last ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:12.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その強運がどこまで続くかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Is that all you've got, Senpai ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなもんですか 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.00,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I won't run or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は逃げも隠れもしない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.86,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I won't lose that easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単には沈みませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.86,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...so throw everything you've\Ngot at me, Hojo Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,来るなら来い 北条凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたの 拓海くん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.50,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Takumi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.21,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,You spaced out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先からぼっとしちゃて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:43.50,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm concerned about that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:43.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あ いや ちょっと先の電話の事が気になって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.50,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,About an impersonator ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,偽物の話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん ごめん 電話していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.48,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can I make a phone call ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.70,def2,..MIKA...,0,0,0,,Sure, no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいよ そんな事気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.00,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll be back in a bit.{Only for a while.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:01.80,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Hello ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.72,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Oh, Fujiwara, what's up \Nat this time of night ?{late ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした藤原 こんな時間に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.94,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Oh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん あぁ その件か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:14.44,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,Sounds like it's Ryosuke's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん どうやら 涼介の車らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.00,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや お前は何も心配するな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:22.21,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,We don't know where he is, or what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこにいるのかも分からないし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしているのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.55,def2,FUMIHIRO.,0,0,0,,I'll hand you over to Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 今啓介に替わる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.00,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Hello, Fujiwara ? Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし 藤原か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく聴け
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:36.50,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}You don't have to worry about my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴のことなら心配なんかしなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:41.51,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,He's not so weak that he \Nneeds you to worry about him.{He's so tough that he \Ndoesn't need your concern.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴はお前に心配されるほど柔じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.00,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,Don't worry about this, and just focus\Non preparations for the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,気にしないで最終戦の準備に集中しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,女なんかと遊んでる場合じゃないぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.63,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}This isn't the time to be\Ngoofing around with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:56.20,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Trust my brother, and don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴を信じろ 心配ない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.37,def2,.TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.01,def2,.KEISUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:57.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:12.46,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クッソ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:15.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言えません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:19.54,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I can't say.\NIt has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 貴方に関係のない事だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:24.26,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,But I can't be satisfied until you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞かなければ 俺は納得できない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.77,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,You love someone else, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,好きな男がいるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:31.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Tell me the name of the\Nguy who took you from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺からお前を奪った男の名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:39.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.21,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Who is he ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.18,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.84,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,How could you be so selfish ?{Look what you've done !}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんて勝手の真似をしてくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.45,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,Are you going to destroy everything ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全てを打ち壊す気か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:08.91,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,Everything from my company's\Nexistence to your carefree college life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私の会社が今あるも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:08.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前がのうのうと学生生活を送っていられるのも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.40,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,{subete}...is owed to Director Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:12.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全て北条院長のおかげだと言う事は知っているだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.58,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,{subete}You know that, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.70,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,Change your clothes, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:16.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,急いで着替えなさい 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.21,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,We're going to visit him and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今から一緒に先方に謝りに行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:24.41,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,If we apologize sincerely,\Nthe Director should forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誠心誠意謝罪をすれば許してくださるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:27.62,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,I've talked to Rin, and he had the same idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,凛くんとも話したが そう言ってくれているぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤです 私は行きません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:31.46,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,No, I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:36.90,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,Enough is enough !\NHow much are you going to trouble me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減にしないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこまで困らせれば気がすむんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私の言う事を聞きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.10,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前自身のためでもあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.10,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,This is for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.96,def2,.FATHER..,0,0,0,,You have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以外に選択肢などない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.35,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I don't want to go, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行きたくないよ パパ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでも 行きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:52.05,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I don't want to go,\Neven if I have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.92,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ryosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがはRB26
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:13.64,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The RB26 is impressive. \NIt must be making at least 650 HP.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,650馬力は出ている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:16.21,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'll be out-accelerated\Non a long straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:16.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ストレートも長いと ねじ込まれてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまんな涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.70,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sorry, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.89,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This time, there's nowhere to run.{place to escape.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんどこそ逃げ場はない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:41.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,情けない 何も出来ないとは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.30,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}How pathetic.\NI can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,指をくわえて見ているだけか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.77,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&} All I can do is watch ?!{just to keep watching ?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:55.65,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This time there's no bank to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は駆け上がる所もない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガードレールのその先は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.04,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Beyond the guard rail is a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,崖だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,立て直した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.35,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He recovered ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.24,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The Grim Reaper's fatal \Nside press didn't work ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:19.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死神渾身のサイドプレスが不発
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何が起こった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.36,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What just happened ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.31,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{hayai}The speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,FCの進入スピードが速すぎるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.38,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The FC's cornering speed is very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,防御は絶対に不可能だと思われていたサイドプレスが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:37.20,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The side press was believed to be\Ninescapable, but it was completely nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,完璧に破られた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見切られた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:44.14,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He dodged my attack by releasing\Nthe side G-force to absorb the impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:44.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶつける瞬間にGを逃がして襲撃を吸収しやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:48.70,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why can't I shoot Ryosuke down ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介を撃ち落せないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,死神の攻撃に対して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:56.40,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If you follow the basics of slow-in and fast-out,\Nyou'll become a victim of the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スローインファーストアウトの基本を守っていては餌食になる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.89,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{tachiagari}You sacrificed the exit speed\Nfor a high-speed approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち上がりを犠牲にしてのハイスピードアプローチか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:05.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても相手の動きがよく見えている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.85,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}On top of that, he sees his\Nopponent's moves very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:09.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対絶命のピンチにも動じないあの精神力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:10.18,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{zettai}He's so strong-minded that he\Ndoesn't flinch at dire circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:12.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心を閉じる事無く開きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:15.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{kokoro}Instead of resisting, he remains open\Nto fear and anger, and lets them go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,恐怖や怒りを心に留めない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:19.80,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{are}That's the ideal Zero mindset\NI've been trying to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれこそ俺が目指す理想的なゼロの心だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にはない何かを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.62,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's shown me something I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男は体現している
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,素晴らしいよ 高橋涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.50,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're incredible, Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:33.99,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No matter how fast the Grim Reaper's car is,\Nhe's no match for you in a normal race.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら速い車でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まともなバトルなら死神が勝てる相手では無かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心のありようがまるで違う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:41.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Their mindsets are totally different, and the\NGrim Reaper looks noticeably impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あからさまに死神の背中に焦りを見える
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:46.85,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{dakara}That's why, with the GT-R still trailing\Nbehind, the situation is even more dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:46.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今GTRが後ろにいることの意味が重い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:59.90,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I've never met Hojo Gou of Sidewinder, but\NHojo Rin was three years senior to me in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:54.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーの北条豪とは まったく面識はないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:59.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北条凛は大学の三年先輩にあたる人なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は北条先輩を助けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:06.65,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I want to save Hojo Rin, because\Nboth of us suffer from the same pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人と俺は 同じ苦しみを抱えている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:10.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ この件は逃げずに受けとめる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.30,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,That's why I can't run away,\Nand must face this head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが俺自身のために必要な事でもあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.50,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,I have to do it for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:20.47,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,The Hojo Rin I knew was sensitive and smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:18.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が知っている北条先輩は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,繊細で頭のきれる人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は何もかも分かっていて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:28.60,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,He knew everything, but couldn't\Naccept it, so he shut himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:28.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっていながら 納得出来ずに閉じこもっているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,キッカケが必要なだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,He just needs a chance, and I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はあの人を信じる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言葉というのは 便利だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:40.20,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Words are convenient, but powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無力なものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.40,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Sometimes you can convey a message\Nthrough means other than words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言葉に頼らないほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:43.25,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,伝わることもあると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,難しいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:48.43,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,What you said is very complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介さんのいう事は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:52.78,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't understand why it has to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜこのタイミングなのかがわかりません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.25,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実の兄弟なワケだし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:58.97,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,Since they're brothers, Sidewinder and the Grim \NReaper might be collaborating behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サイドワインダーと死神が裏で連携しているとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:03.00,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,{Kanagawa}This could be a trap in order to gain\Nan advantage in the final Kanagawa battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:03.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神奈川最終戦を有利に戦うための罠だとも考えられますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:06.79,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,That's not likely, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのセンはないよ 松本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.42,def2,MATSUMOTO,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言い切れるんですか はっきり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理由があるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:17.11,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Hojo Rin picked this date\Nfor a reason, an obvious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:15.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北条凛が今日という日を指定してきた事には
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はっきりと理由が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は香織の二回目の命日だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.86,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Today's the second anniversary of Kaori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.76,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's only been two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの日からまだ二年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が許せないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:35.31,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What I can't stand is that \Nyou've recovered and moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前がとっくに立ち直って前に進んでいることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:41.40,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}How can you be so cold-hearted ?\NWas it so easy for you to forget ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,薄情な男だな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど簡単に忘れてしまえるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の香織への気持ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:46.58,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's the extent of your feelings for Kaori ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その程度の物だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:48.61,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,傷の深さは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:59.71,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...you shouldn't let the depth of the scar, depth of sadness,\Nor the intensity of your despair keep you from moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しみの大きさは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望して立ち止まってしまうこととは別なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなに苦しくても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:07.55,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No matter how strong the pain is, \Nit's our duty to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:06.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前に進むことは俺たちの義務だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴方こそ間違っている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:11.51,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're wrong for running away from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはただの現実逃避だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ 涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shut up, Ryosuke !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.50,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're the one who's running away !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前こそ逃げている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.19,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Both of us are responsible for Kaori's suicide !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,香織の自殺は俺たち二人の責任だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:26.23,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Don't forget that, Ryosuke. \NI'll never let you forget that !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れるな 涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れる事は絶対許さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,忘れってなんかいない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.10,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I haven't forgotten, nor run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げてもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.60,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It has never escaped my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,片時も心から消えることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ 進むことが俺の答えだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.99,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's why I made my\Nchoice to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:45.55,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{konna}You think she wishes for\Nus to keep fighting like this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうに俺たちがいがみ合うことが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女の望みだとでもいうんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.27,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{konna}This will only make her sad !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:46.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悲しませるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分からないのか 北条先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.63,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{wakaranai}Why can't you understand this, Hojo ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:52.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,目を覚ませ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.30,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please, snap out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴方が香織さんの為に俺を追い詰めるというなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:17:01.11,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If you intend to drive me into despair, \NI'll wake you up for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は彼女の為にも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴方の目を覚まさせてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.50,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:13.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキの効きを確かめるようなペダルの踏み方が頻繁に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:13.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's checking the brakes' \Neffectiveness far too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,フィーリングがおかしいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.90,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Is the pedal feeling weird ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.17,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Is there something wrong with the GT-R's brakes ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,GTRのブレーキに何か異変が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,元気で今もいてくれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:31.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I just wished she were alive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけでよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,香織 お前は俺にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:39.52,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaori, you're the best woman I ever \Nmet, no matter what others say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最高の女なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰がなんと言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,例え俺の物でなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:46.54,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Even if you're not mine, so long \Nas you're happy, I'd be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が幸せなら それでよかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,柔らかな髪 吸い込まれそうな眼差し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:52.30,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Soft hair, a breathtaking gaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,透き通るように白い肌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...translucent white skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:59.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,細い体 しなやかなライン
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:18:00.17,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...slim body, and gentle curves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にとってお前はアートだった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.69,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{ore}To me, you're like a work of art. {He's so creepy!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:08.07,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But you're not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けれども お前は もういない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんと えげつないサイドプレスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:16.75,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}My god, what a nasty side press !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:26.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Instead of thrusting out the nose, he put his\Ncar's body against the other to push it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,突き飛ばすのではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ボディを密着させてグイグイと押しこんでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,交わす交わせないの次元じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.69,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is not a matter of dodging or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな死神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You can't be serious{Don't be ridiculous}, Grim Reaper !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,谷に懸かる橋の上だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.29,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're on the bridge over the valley !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキを踏んでノーズを引っ込ぬいた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.40,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He hit the brakes to pull the nose out !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.96,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Both cars will lose control at the same time !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二台の姿勢が同時に崩れる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すさまじいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.33,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:03.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アンダーステアのGTRが縁石に接触し
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:03.30,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The under-steered GT-R hit the curb...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オーバーステアのFCがフルカウンターでラインをクロスさせた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:07.20,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...while the over-steered FC crossed\Nthe line with full counter steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:11.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで果たし合いのような殺伐としたドッグファイトでありながら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:12.05,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No doubt, this is a deadly dogfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハイレベルな技術と技術の応酬が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:19.00,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But I've been witnessing a beautiful exchange\Nof splendid skills over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:18.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,宝石のように煌く瞬間を 何度も魅せつけられるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.46,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}How I pity you, Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だぜ死神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:28.09,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{sorehodo}With such skills, why do you have to turn\Nyour precious car into a lethal weapon ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それほどのスキルを持ちながら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ大切な車を凶器を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.31,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,落とせないのか これだけ攻めても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:33.17,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't get him even if I attack that hard ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,みかけによらず愚直な男だ 涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.68,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You're foolishly honest,\Ndespite your looks, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:39.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げずに受け止めてくれているというわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:39.39,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Are you trying to play along with me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.89,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}For what ? For whom ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:42.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何のために
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰のためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,またか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.40,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Again ! Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:50.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに何か異変が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.96,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The braking distance is getting longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,制動距離も伸びてきている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.80,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's fatal to have a brake problem \Non the downhill of this course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:58.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このコースの下りでブレーキトラブルは致命的だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:02.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その状況でなぜアクセルを踏んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:02.36,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}So why is your foot still on \Nthe gas in these circumstances ?!{Why do you keep accelerating\Nin these circumstances ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介くんの夢って何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.66,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}What is your dream, Ryosuke ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,優秀な医者に成ること
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.79,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,To become a good doctor ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:21.81,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Sounds good, and I admire it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,立派だと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夢とは言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:24.26,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,...you can hardly call it a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:26.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とても現実的な目標だと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.26,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,It's just a practical goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,男の人には夢があっていいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.67,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{otoko}I think men should be eager to chase dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:31.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あたし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.76,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Mine ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:38.76,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Girls are different.\NI can live with practical goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.75,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,女の子は違うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,現実的な目標だけで生きていけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:44.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,現実に背を向けて夢に向かって行けるほど強くないから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:45.10,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I'm not strong enough to turn away\Nfrom reality to pursue my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:50.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 夢を負うのは男の人だけの特権だと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:51.24,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{dakara}I think men have the privilege \Nof being able to chase dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:58.42,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,{honto}I wish I could keep watching\Nit with the person I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントは ずっと好きな人の側にいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:58.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと一緒にそれを見ていられたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夢 か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.47,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:17.31,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What terrible under-steering.\NThe front tires have no grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,酷いアンダーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,フロントタイヤのクリップがもうない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:21.85,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The brakes are even worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:19.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だがそれ以上に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:22.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ブレーキはもっと駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:25.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誤算だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:30.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I never thought this game would last this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:30.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このゲームがこれほど長引くとはまったく考えていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:35.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの下りはサーキットを走るよりもブレーキに負担がかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:34.96,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This downhill puts more stress\Non the brakes than the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:44.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このコーナーの出口に 最終の緊急退避所があるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:44.30,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There's one more emergency \Nescape area beyond the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.95,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If you can't stop, use it, Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれないのならそこに逃げろ 死神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.10,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You've done enough !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう十分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだ 行け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.34,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Now, use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:02.70,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You idiot !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,バーカーヤロウ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.66,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The GT-R's pace is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,GTRのペースがおかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,考えられることは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.66,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The possible cause is the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らくブレーキ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:17.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まずいな どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.83,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Damn, what should I do ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:24.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前には失望したよ 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.84,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}I'm disappointed in you, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:26.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,好きにすればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:27.65,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:31.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もオヤジも今度のことでは不愉快の気分にさせられた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:32.72,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,This whole thing has displeased\Nboth my father and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後で後悔することに成るだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:35.00,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,You'll regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:42.54,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,I hate to say this, but your father's\Nbusiness will suffer from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌な言い方になるが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:42.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の父親の事業もこの先苦しいだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:48.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も俺を選ばなかったことを絶対に後悔する時が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:48.67,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,Someday, you'll regret \Nthat you didn't choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,深い意味は無かった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:56.07,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It didn't have any deep meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:58.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悔し紛れに口走った ただの戯言だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:22:59.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I couldn't help saying such a foolish\Nthing because I was so frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:04.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,香織 お前を追い詰めたのは俺なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:04.42,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kaori, was it me who\Ndrove you into a corner ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけインをカットしてもまだラインが膨らむ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.38,0:23:14.90,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It slid outward that much even\Nthough it had an inside line.{a line so close to the inside of the corner.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:17.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,制動力がもうほとんどないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:17.35,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It may have lost most\Nof its braking potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなれば死神に残されている手段は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:23.40,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}All that's left is for the Grim\NReaper to launch a suicide attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:23.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自爆とも言える体当たりしかあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げろ 高橋涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:28.24,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Run, Takahashi Ryosuke. Shake him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを振りきっていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:32.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だが今の死神が正気じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:32.52,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm afraid the Grim Reaper has lost his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,付き合うことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:37.80,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You don't have to continue playing his\Ngame. Get out of his attack range.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:37.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,射程距離の外へ逃げってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:45.49,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why did you release the accelerator\Nway before the braking point ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:45.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜブレーキングポイントの遥か手前でアクセルを抜くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:47.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だぜここで減速する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:47.68,def2,..IKEDA..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why did you slow down here ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:53.20,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:53.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:55.68,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What're you doing, Ryosuke ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:55.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしている涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:00.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止められるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:03.76,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You can't stop the heavy body of the R32.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:03.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この重いR32の車体を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.71,0:24:07.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちのブレーキはもう完全に抜けとるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:07.92,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}My brakes are completely gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:11.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二台分の車重を受けとめるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:13.86,def2,...RIN...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Your FC's brakes can't\Ntake the weight of two cars !
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:13.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そのFCのブレーキでは無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:21.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さよなら 涼介君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:21.58,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.46,0:24:23.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:26.30,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,What are you talking about ?\NKaori, where are you now ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,香織さん 今どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:28.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今までありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:33.34,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.\NAlthough it was brief, I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:33.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,短い間だけど 楽しかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:35.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこにいるか言ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.23,0:24:37.45,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,Tell me where you are.\NI'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:37.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐにそっちにいくから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:43.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君に会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:46.12,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,I'm glad I met you, Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.32,0:24:46.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,涼介君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.39,0:24:51.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さよなら
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.52,0:24:51.54,def2,..KAORI..,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.97,0:25:01.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二台の軸がズレていて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.04,0:25:03.71,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's so hard to maintain control\Nbecause the two cars are misaligned.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:03.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,バランスが取りにくい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.64,0:25:05.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,取り返しのつかないミスだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:05.80,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's an unrecoverable mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:08.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,制動力をマックスに立ち上げられない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:08.90,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't get the maximum braking ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.02,0:25:10.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:13.15,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's no good, we aren't slowing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:12.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スピードが落ちってない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.05,0:25:14.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:14.31,def2,.RYOSUKE.,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can't stop !
